      "span_text": "To identify the transcriptional network responsible for layer subtype specification downstream of Foxg1, we used previous datasets in which the temporal cohorts of CD133 ϩ cells after Foxg1 induction in vivo were FACS sorted and subject to Affymetrix high-density oligonucleotide arrays for Mus musculus (Mouse Genome 430 2.0), which contained 45,038 probes"
